relationship I count on.

595
00:26:36,411 --> 00:26:39,179
And now I'm not sure
if I just screwed that up

596
00:26:39,248 --> 00:26:41,815
or freed myself
from its limitations.

597
00:26:44,586 --> 00:26:47,020
The one thing I
know for sure, though,

598
00:26:48,190 --> 00:26:50,523
