599
00:26:50,592 --> 00:26:53,992
Dr. Kepner, we
asked you a question.

600
00:26:54,930 --> 00:26:58,232
Yes, I would do a palliative
endoscopic stenting.

601
00:26:58,300 --> 00:27:01,535
