731
00:33:14,109 --> 00:33:17,411
I think we've had enough of
an education today, Dr. Yang.

732
00:33:18,763 --> 00:33:21,464
But there's still 20 minutes.

733
00:33:21,533 --> 00:33:22,613
No need.

734
00:33:24,486 --> 00:33:25,718
Oh.

735
00:33:25,788 --> 00:33:27,120
Best of luck.

736
00:33:32,344 --> 00:33:33,743
I'd do a biopsy.

737
00:33:33,811 --> 00:33:36,946
Path shows LCIS. What's your
best mastectomy approach?

738
00:33:37,015 --> 00:33:38,692
I'd make a periareolar incision

739
00:33:38,716 --> 00:33:40,756
to preserve the
inframammary fold.

740
00:33:42,170 --> 00:33:44,921
But wait. Did you say LCIS?

741
00:33:44,990 --> 00:33:47,073
Yes, lobular carcinoma in situ.

742
00:33:47,142 --> 00:33:48,319
You wouldn't do a mastectomy.

743
00:33:48,343 --> 00:33:49,720
You'd observe and repeat mammos.

744
00:33:49,744 --> 00:33:51,961
You already did a
skin-sparing mastectomy.

745
00:33:53,065 --> 00:33:54,308
That was a trick question.

746
00:33:54,332 --> 00:33:56,277
You had all the facts to answer.

747
00:33:56,301 --> 00:33:57,611
Yeah, but my answer was wrong.

748
00:33:57,635 --> 00:34:00,048
I'm gonna fail because
of a trick question?

749
00:34:00,072 --> 00:34:02,172
The questions are designed
to get your response...

750
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,334
You got to be kidding me?

751
00:34:03,358 --> 00:34:04,535
You missed your first session.

752
00:34:04,559 --> 00:34:06,543
You're lucky to be
even getting this chance.

753
00:34:06,611 --> 00:34:09,629
Yeah, I missed my first session
for the best freakin' reason.

754
00:34:09,698 --> 00:34:11,481
I was with a patient.

755
00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:14,128
For months with this kid
who doesn't have a chance.

756
00:34:14,152 --> 00:34:15,618
Not a chance.

757
00:34:15,687 --> 00:34:18,287
And we give them a
chance and we try everything,

758
00:34:18,356 --> 00:34:20,168
and then when there's
nothing left to do,

759
00:34:20,192 --> 00:34:23,654
I'm supposed to just walk
away from his mother?

760
00:34:23,678 --> 00:34:26,730
